# Zero-Trust Identity

- Use `security.get_identity_manager()` — auto-detects cloud runtime
- AWS: IRSA / instance profile · Azure: managed identity · GCP: Workload Identity
- OCI: resource principal · IBM: Trusted Profile · Alibaba: ECS RAM role · PCF: UAA + CredHub
- Secrets in vault services only — never in git, Dockerfile, or MCP tool args
- Skill: `zero-trust-identity-and-secrets`
